snippet.title: Bubsy in Fractured Furry Tales - Atari Jaguar
snippet.description:
Bubsy for the Jag isn't exactly the most sought-after game, however it's really only because of its difficulty.
There is, however, one Jaguar fan who can seriously take on Bubsy and he's done a bunch of videos for each level, if I remember correctly. doctorclu is the Bubsy master and nothing can stand in his way. Search for him here on youtube.
I found the game fun for the little that I played it. It has some difficult controls, but docclu makes it look easy. There are some nice pre-rendered graphics as well.
Give it a try.
